title: Nasrabad, Anbarabad
text: Nasrabad (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as Naşrābād) is a village in <a href="Mohammadabad%20Rural%20District%20%28Anbarabad%20County%29">Mohammadabad Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Anbarabad%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Anbarabad%20County">Anbarabad County</a>, <a href="Kerman%20Province">Kerman Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 13, in 4 families.
